a-rodrigo-chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/olivia-rodrigo-chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/olivia-rodrigo-chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/olivia-rodrigo-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/olivia-rodrigo-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>透露，查<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a>与她分享了关于成名的“很多建议”——看看这位“吸血鬼”歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/olivia-rodrigo-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3756151">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 伦敦现场演出：很可能是 2024 年最有趣的巡演</a></strong></li></ul><p>在过去的几年里，奥利维亚·罗德里戈和查普尔·罗恩见证了名气的迅速崛起。两人都有相似的经历，因此建立了友谊， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-brings-out-former-opener-chappell-roan-for-hot-to-go-in-california-3785457">并多次一起演出</a>，并轮流分享如何应对名气和娱乐业压力的建议。 </p><figure id="attachment_3806831" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806831" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806831" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/chappell-roan-olivia-rodrigo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806831" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩和奥利维亚·罗德里戈一起表演。图片来源：Christopher Polk/Billboard via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>最近，罗恩与罗德里戈一起参加了罗德里戈<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-energetic-trailer-for-olivia-rodrigos-guts-concert-film-3805350">为 Netflix 制作的新音乐会电影《胆量》</a>的全球首映式。在参加首映活动时， <em>《告示牌》</em>询问罗德里戈他们给彼此提供的建议。这位“Good 4 U”歌手很快承认，她不确定自己是否向罗恩提供了很多帮助，但罗恩对保持她的心理健康很有帮助。</p><p>罗德里戈对<em>《公告牌》</em>说：“她实际上给了我很多关于照顾自己以及在一个有时令人难以承受的行业中做我自己的建议。我真的很欣赏她。如果我给她任何建议，我不太确定。但我从她身上得到了很多。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBlCHR1R8-w/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="trans